Description of heavy exotic resonances as molecular states using phenomenological Lagrangians

We report progress, in last decade in description of heavy exotic resonances using phenomenological Lagrangians — of a hadronic molecular approach developed by the Tübingen–Beijing group. In particular, we present a comprehensive analysis of decays properties of exotic heavy mesons and baryons.
